            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Deuteronomy.11:1-12:32",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDeuteronomy%2011%3A1-12%3A32%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_1%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDeuteronomy%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20must%20love%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20and%20always%20obey%20his%20requirements%2C%20decrees%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20commands.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_2%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20now%20to%20your%20children%2C%20who%20have%20never%20experienced%20the%20discipline%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20or%20seen%20his%20greatness%20and%20his%20strong%20hand%20and%20powerful%20arm.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_3%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20see%20the%20miraculous%20signs%20and%20wonders%20he%20performed%20in%20Egypt%20against%20Pharaoh%20and%20all%20his%20land.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_4%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20see%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20did%20to%20the%20armies%20of%20Egypt%20and%20to%20their%20horses%20and%20chariots%26%23x2014%3Bhow%20he%20drowned%20them%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Esea%20of%20reeds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20as%20they%20were%20chasing%20you.%20He%20destroyed%20them%2C%20and%20they%20have%20not%20recovered%20to%20this%20very%20day!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_5%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYour%20children%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20see%20how%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20cared%20for%20you%20in%20the%20wilderness%20until%20you%20arrived%20here.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_6%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20see%20what%20he%20did%20to%20Dathan%20and%20Abiram%20(the%20sons%20of%20Eliab%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20Reuben)%20when%20the%20earth%20opened%20its%20mouth%20in%20the%20Israelite%20camp%20and%20swallowed%20them%2C%20along%20with%20their%20households%20and%20tents%20and%20every%20living%20thing%20that%20belonged%20to%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_7%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20you%20have%20seen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20perform%20all%20these%20mighty%20deeds%20with%20your%20own%20eyes!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_8%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Blessings%20of%20Obedience%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BTherefore%2C%20be%20careful%20to%20obey%20every%20command%20I%20am%20giving%20you%20today%2C%20so%20you%20may%20have%20strength%20to%20go%20in%20and%20take%20over%20the%20land%20you%20are%20about%20to%20enter.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_9%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20you%20obey%2C%20you%20will%20enjoy%20a%20long%20life%20in%20the%20land%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20swore%20to%20give%20to%20your%20ancestors%20and%20to%20you%2C%20their%20descendants%26%23x2014%3Ba%20land%20flowing%20with%20milk%20and%20honey!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_10%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20land%20you%20are%20about%20to%20enter%20and%20take%20over%20is%20not%20like%20the%20land%20of%20Egypt%20from%20which%20you%20came%2C%20where%20you%20planted%20your%20seed%20and%20made%20irrigation%20ditches%20with%20your%20foot%20as%20in%20a%20vegetable%20garden.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_11%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ERather%2C%20the%20land%20you%20will%20soon%20take%20over%20is%20a%20land%20of%20hills%20and%20valleys%20with%20plenty%20of%20rain%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_12%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3Ea%20land%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20cares%20for.%20He%20watches%20over%20it%20through%20each%20season%20of%20the%20year!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_13%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIf%20you%20carefully%20obey%20the%20commands%20I%20am%20giving%20you%20today%2C%20and%20if%20you%20love%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20and%20serve%20him%20with%20all%20your%20heart%20and%20soul%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_14%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3Ethen%20he%20will%20send%20the%20rains%20in%20their%20proper%20seasons%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20early%20and%20late%20rains%26%23x2014%3Bso%20you%20can%20bring%20in%20your%20harvests%20of%20grain%2C%20new%20wine%2C%20and%20olive%20oil.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_15%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20give%20you%20lush%20pastureland%20for%20your%20livestock%2C%20and%20you%20yourselves%20will%20have%20all%20you%20want%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_16%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20be%20careful.%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20let%20your%20heart%20be%20deceived%20so%20that%20you%20turn%20away%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20serve%20and%20worship%20other%20gods.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_17%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20you%20do%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20anger%20will%20burn%20against%20you.%20He%20will%20shut%20up%20the%20sky%20and%20hold%20back%20the%20rain%2C%20and%20the%20ground%20will%20fail%20to%20produce%20its%20harvests.%20Then%20you%20will%20quickly%20die%20in%20that%20good%20land%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20giving%20you.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_11_18%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20commit%20yourselves%20wholeheartedly%20to%20these%20words%20of%20mine.%20Tie%20them%20to%20your%20hands%20and%20wear%20them%20on%20your%20forehead%20as%20